                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">List of persons now resident in the legation of the United
                        States in Asuncion,</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The minister, wife, and child; Mrs. Leite Pereira; Carlos Meincke, private
                    secretary; Kate Leahy; George F. Masterman, medical attendant; Porter C. Bliss,
                    translator; George Hamilton, Baltazar Carreras, Bazilio Jara, Melchora Jara,
                    Lucia Rivas, (lavandera.)</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <date calendar="gregorian" when="1868-08-13">
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">August 13</hi>, 1868</date>.</dateline>
                </closer>
